  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique, once used, grants two charges that can be used to amplify your physical strength. You can concentrate as a swift action and spend up to 5 Chakra to gain as many charges. When you run out of charges, the technique ends. Charges can be spent to gain a +1 bonus to weapon damage per charge spent for 1 round, up to +5. Every 2 charges spent in a round increases your base carrying capacity by 50% that round.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to gain an additional charge.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step increases the maximum possible bonus to weapon damage by +1.<br><br>The first, third and fifth step increase the amount of Chakra you can spend when concentrating to gain charges, by 1 each.<br><br>The fifth step requires ECL 12 to achieve, and allows you to ignore any hardness of 8 or lower while this technique is in effect.</p>\n",
